'''Aebea''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive. They were about a [[Meter/Legends|meter]] long, and were used during the [[Swarm War]] as airborne fighters. During the [[Cold War (Galactic Republic–Sith Empire)|Cold War]], the [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Joiner]] [[Vector Hyllus]] was taught by the Aebea how to suppress the pheromonic Joiner bond, allowing him to temporarily separate himself from the Colony hivemind.

